Q) How many nodes should be in k8s cluster and how much cpu and memory on there? How you can calculate this?
ans : for that first need to ask application teams like how many micro services you will deplpy in application and how many replicas you need.
      and each replica need like 5 GB ram or cpu etc.
	  
	  
	  memory: 256 GB
