	  Quota type:
	  1) compute quota: cpu/memory when you want to limit cpu/memory on containers.
	  2) resource/objective quota: pod/deplpyment/rc/rs 
	  
	      use case: multiple team work on their projcect on pods and after completed his project they forge to delete pods or objects. 
		             I mean they wasting resources and increase etcd data storage and maybe also impact etcd performance or query latency because of heavy data.
					 
					( generally it use in market prospestive to charge from customer as per usage)
					
	      Note: resource quota only apply on namespace.
		  
